  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_887_2",
    "text": "讨论与思考",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.33925049309664695,
      0.11228070175438597,
      0.44970414201183434,
      0.1314866112650046
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_887",
    "order": 2
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_887_3",
    "text": "在《物理1》的开篇中，我们曾问：假如有一种完全没有摩擦的 “理想热机”，它的效率能达到100%吗？现在，你是否有所领悟？",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.33530571992110453,
      0.1602954755309326,
      0.8944773175542406,
      0.20313942751615882
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_887",
    "order": 3
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_887_4",
    "text": "本节开始提出的设想为什么无法实现？",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.3727810650887574,
      0.20757156048014774,
      0.7120315581854043,
      0.2267774699907664
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_887",
    "order": 4
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_887_5",
    "text": "科学家正在研究一种新技术：利用海洋中不同深度的温度差 驱动热机。这为什么是可行的？",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.33530571992110453,
      0.23120960295475532,
      0.893491124260355,
      0.27479224376731304
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_887",
    "order": 5
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_887_1",
    "text": "Camm 179% 1832).法医物型学家、工科 师华业于出聚综台工科学 税，1824个提出了关于热机 的卜诺循坏和卜话定理。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.09171597633136094,
      0.2984302862419206,
      0.29980276134122286,
      0.38337950138504157
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_887",
    "order": 6
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_887_6",
    "text": "1851年，英国物理学家威廉·汤姆生（即开尔文勋爵）从热机 的工作特点山发，总结出热力学第二定律的另种表述：不可能 从单·热源吸收热量并把它全部用来做功，而不引起其他变化。 这种表述称为开尔文表述。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.3343195266272189,
      0.3752539242843952,
      0.8964497041420119,
      0.46685133887349956
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_887",
    "order": 7
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_887_7",
    "text": "当能量转化与守恒定律对“第一类永动机”做出“不可能制 成”的判决后，历史1曾有许多人精心构思，想设计出一种从单一 热源吸热，并把所吸热量除用于克服摩擦做功外全部用来对外做 功的机器，也就是说，一种效率达到100%的热机。这种机器称为 “第二类永动机”。“第二类水动机”并不违背能量转化与守恒定 律，但根据热力学第定律的开尔文表述，同样可以做山判决： “第二类永动机”也是不可能制成的。而这正是热力学第二定律的 又一种表述。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.3343195266272189,
      0.47054478301015695,
      0.8964497041420119,
      0.6574330563250231
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_887",
    "order": 8
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_887_8",
    "text": "案例分析",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.33925049309664695,
      0.6847645429362881,
      0.4289940828402367,
      0.7054478301015698
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_887",
    "order": 9
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_887_9",
    "text": "案例炎炎夏1，两位同学在充满凉意的空调室内，就空调 机的工作过程是否遵循热力学第二定律的问题发生了争论。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.3343195266272189,
      0.7320406278855033,
      0.8954635108481263,
      0.775623268698061
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_887",
    "order": 10
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_887_10",
    "text": "位同学说：空调机工作时，不断地把热量从室内传到室外， 即从低温物休传到高温物体，可见它并不遵循热力学第二定律。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.33530571992110453,
      0.7793167128347184,
      0.8944773175542406,
      0.8236380424746076
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_887",
    "order": 11
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_887_11",
    "text": "另一位同学说：热力学第定律是热力学系统的普遍规律， 空调机的工作过程不可能违反它。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.33530571992110453,
      0.827331486611265,
      0.8944773175542406,
      0.8709141274238227
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_887",
    "order": 12
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_887_12",
    "text": "两人各执一词，都无法使对方信服。请你对他们的论点作出 评价。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.3333333333333333,
      0.8746075715604802,
      0.8944773175542406,
      0.9181902123730379
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_887",
    "order": 13
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_887_13",
    "text": "分析空调机和电冰箱都是制冷机，它们的工作原理基木相 同。为了使于分析，我们以电冰箱为研究对象，认识它的基本结构",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.3333333333333333,
      0.9226223453370268,
      0.8954635108481263,
      0.9662049861495845
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_887",
    "order": 14
  }
]